  "title": "How do educational and occupational resources relate to the timing of family formation? A couple analysis of the Netherlands",
  "abstract": "Fertility research often uses data from women only. This can bias the results if the effects of education and occupation on fertility are dependent upon the characteristics of the male partner. Using retrospective life-course information from both partners",
